App Name: What Type of Girl Are You?

Through a variety of questions about your preferences, lifestyle, and perceptions, the app guides you to a deeper understanding of what type of girl you resonate with most. From a fashionable trendsetter to a driven change-maker, each outcome is crafted to reflect your unique traits and offer tailored insights.
